{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sizeHeightCursorUnselected","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena","text":"SizeSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeswitchcomponenttokensprovider\/sizeheightcursorunselected"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token dimensions._5xsmall"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sizeHeightCursorUnselected"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SizeSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B34ThemeSwitchComponentTokensProviderC26sizeHeightCursorUnselectedSdvp","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"title":"sizeHeightCursorUnselected"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider\/sizeHeightCursorUnselected"},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeswitchcomponenttokensprovider","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of switch"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"switch \/ toggle"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSSwitch","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSwitchComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwitchComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"switch \/ toggle","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Switch","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpacesSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":") ,  dimensions (","type":"text"},{"code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sizes (","type":"text"},{"code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"), borders (","type":"text"},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":") and opacities (","type":"text"},{"code":"AllOpacitiySemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider/sizeHeightCursorUnselected":{"type":"topic","title":"sizeHeightCursorUnselected","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"sizeHeightCursorUnselected"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena","text":"SizeSemanticToken"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token dimensions._5xsmall"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeswitchcomponenttokensprovider\/sizeheightcursorunselected","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider\/sizeHeightCursorUnselected"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"image"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"}}}